<h2>Working At PPC</h2>

  <p>At PPC we believe people are our most valuable asset. PPC strives to place itself as the employer of choice within the vocational rehabilitation industry.  </p>

    <p>The company offers a challenging and rewarding career and seeks to attract and retain the best employees in our industry. We also aim to provide a workplace that allows everyone to perform at his or her best.</p>

  <p class="listpara">The qualities we value in our employees include:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Professionalism</li>
  <li>A focus on achieving outcomes for all clients</li>
  <li>Self-motivation, integrity and respect</li>
  <li>The ability to work independently and in a team</li>
</ul>
  <p class="listpara">We employ professionals with qualifications in the following fields:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Vocational Rehabilitation</li>
  <li>Psychology</li>
  <li>Social Work</li>
  <li>Nursing</li>
  <li>Human Resources</li>
  <li>Occupational Therapy</li>
  <li>Physiotherapy</li>
</ul>
  <h2>Benefits</h2>

  <p class="listpara">Some of the benefits of working at PPC include the following:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Opportunities for professional development (i.e. study, support for conferences, long term career planning)</li>
    <li>In-house induction, training, mentoring and support</li>
